                    <span>If you want to see why many people think that Meryl Streep is the greatest film actress on the planet, this is the film to see. The scene where she recalls her 'choice' is absolutely astonishing. It is very difficult to watch, in the same way of the Russian Roulette scene in the rier hut in 'The Deer Hunter'. I rate 'Sophie' as a 4, only because it is so intense and really only suited for adults.</span>
                  
              
